data.description: Fully remodeled 4 bed, 3 bath home w/ dual masters, entertainer's backyard featuring pebble-tech pool, covered patio w/ misters, firepit & bocce court. This Arizona Country Club neighborhood home was extensively updated in 2017 & current owner has added another $50k+ in upgrades since then, including but not limited to new AC, smart home features (fridge, Nest thermostat/camera, Brinks security system), tankless gas water heater, walk in master closet w/ vanity, pantry, coat & linen closet, mature landscaping, upgraded lighting, dimmers & more! Previous owner's remodel included new tile flooring, bathrooms, kitchen, roof, windows, pavers & more. Walking distance to the canal trail, AZCC, Old Town, etc. You won't find this many upgrades in the area for less than $700k, seller expects multiple offers.
